&lt;p&gt;Zustic Query combines the best parts of RTK Query, TanStack Query, and SWR into a tiny (~2KB), powerful package with &lt;strong&gt;zero configuration overhead&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building a small side project or a large-scale application, Zustic Query gives you the tools to manage server state efficiently and elegantly.&lt;/p&gt;

